<title>Chapter 5: SELECT → .Select() — Projections — SQL to C#</title>
<meta name="description" content="Master SELECT projections in SQL and their C# LINQ equivalents. Learn anonymous types, DTOs, computed columns, and what Entity Framework generates under the hood.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Source+Serif+4:wght@300;400;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

:root {
  --bg: #f8f7f3;
  --bg2: #f0ede6;
  --bg3: #e8e4db;
  --white: #ffffff;
  --ink: #1c1a17;
